set.name: Don DiMello Stages 'Cinderella' at the Pasadena Fairytale Theatre
set.article: The show was 'not your typical garbage,' according to Mr. DiMello, and featured a number of liberties taken in the interpretation of the classic story including an extra sister and considerable nudity. Cinderella was triple-cast and spoke simultaneously. The show failed to reach denouement.
